snippet.title: GOLDRUSHERS RELEASE TRAILER
snippet.description:
A Goldrush themed local multiplayer brawler for PC and Mac! 
Play as two competing prospectors trying to fill your safes with precious gold nuggets or other items of value.GOLDRUSHERS will provide fast paced action, wacky antics, and flying horses for your living room. 

http://store.steampowered.com/app/710630/GOLDRUSHERS/
